74
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:27,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How about you go with the other children
and eat your delicious candy back in your room?</font>

75
00:04:30,410 --> 00:04:31,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?  What's wrong?</font>

76
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:39,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>You don't want to go back to the laboratory, do you?!</i></font>

77
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Get out of my way!</i></font>

78
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:44,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Usopp!</i></font>

79
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:46,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Master... please give me candy...</i></font>

